# Linting & Formatting

## ESLint

```json
{
  "@typescript-eslint/no-explicit-any": "error",
  "@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars": "error",
  "no-console": "error",
  "react-hooks/rules-of-hooks": "error",
  "react-hooks/exhaustive-deps": "warn",
  "jsx-a11y/alt-text": "error",
  "jsx-a11y/no-static-element-interactions": "error",
  "jsx-a11y/click-events-have-key-events": "error",
  "import/no-cycle": "error",
  "import/order": ["error", { "groups": ["builtin","external","internal","parent","sibling"], "newlines-between": "always" }]
}
```

Plugins: `@typescript-eslint`, `react-hooks`, `jsx-a11y`, `import`

## Prettier

```json
{ "semi": true, "singleQuote": false, "trailingComma": "all", "printWidth": 100, "tabWidth": 2 }
```

## Enforcement

- No warnings in CI — all treated as errors.
- Format on save in every editor.
- `husky` + `lint-staged` pre-commit hook.
- Import order: builtin → external → internal → parent → sibling (blank lines between).

