# Git Conventions

## Branches

`type/short-kebab-description` — types: `feature`, `fix`, `chore`, `refactor`, `docs`

```
feature/hero-section
fix/mobile-nav-overflow
chore/update-dependencies
```

## Commits — Conventional Commits

`type(scope): lowercase description`

```
feat(hero): add parallax background effect
fix(nav): resolve hamburger not closing on route change
chore(deps): update react-i18next to v14
refactor(services): split into ServiceCard sub-component
```

Types: `feat`, `fix`, `chore`, `refactor`, `docs`, `style`

## Rules

- Every commit passes lint + type-check (enforced by hooks).
- Atomic commits — one logical change each.
- No `WIP` or `temp` on main.
- Squash-merge feature branches.
